00:26:45.534 --> 00:26:46.575
Okay. okay.

423
00:26:46.576 --> 00:26:47.618
I don't...

424
00:26:47.619 --> 00:26:49.578
Okay. okay.

425
00:26:50.664 --> 00:26:52.122
Okay. we'll be okay.

426
00:26:54.793 --> 00:26:55.961
I'm right here.

427
00:26:57.379 --> 00:26:58.505
I'm right here.

428
00:27:02.509 --> 00:27:04.468
I'm right here.

429
00:27:09.849 --> 00:27:11.767
Okay.

