and they didn't come out.

498
00:33:23.389 --> 00:33:25.849
This place got exactly
what it fucking wanted.

499
00:33:25.850 --> 00:33:27.809
Is there any chance
they survived?

500
00:33:27.810 --> 00:33:29.436
How. Kenny?

501
00:33:29.437 --> 00:33:31.063
There's one exit
out of that chamber.

502
00:33:31.064 --> 00:33:34.149
One! If they were alive...

503
00:33:34.150 --> 00:33:36.735
God damn it!

504
00:33:36.736 --> 00:33:38.403
If they were alive.
they'd be here right now.

505
00:33:38.404 --> 00:33:40.447
No. we can't just give up!

506
00:33:40.448 --> 00:33:42.658
All right. then tell me
how to move forward. okay?

507
00:33:42.659 --> 00:33:46.203
Please. Anybody. Tell me!

508
00:33:46.204 --> 00:33:50.248
We just made the sun go down!

509
00:33:50.249 --> 00:33:54.086
We fucking tore a hole in
the goddamn sky with lightning!

510
00:33:54.087 --> 00:33:56.380
Who the fuck
even knows what that means!

511
00:33:56.381 --> 00:33:58.382
So. what are we supposed to do

512
00:33:58.383 --> 00:33:59.675
