make anything better?

513
00:33:59.676 --> 00:34:00.884
Boyd...

514
00:34:00.885 --> 00:34:02.511
We lost three people today!
- Boyd...

515
00:34:02.512 --> 00:34:05.430
- I'm not going... What?!
- Boyd! Stop!

516
00:34:05.431 --> 00:34:06.599
Listen.

517
00:34:10.979 --> 00:34:12.062
Are you...?

518
00:34:13.564 --> 00:34:15.649
